author: RTÉ News
title: US surpasses 700,000 coronavirus cases
description: The United States has passed 700,000 confirmed coronavirus cases, according to a tally maintained by Johns Hopkins University.
content:
The United States has passed 700,000 confirmed coronavirus cases, according to a tally maintained by Johns Hopkins University.
